## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="d9858-130">下面的 C# 示例演示如何枚举中指定的全局编录服务器<xref:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.DirectoryContext>对象，并打印到标准控制台每个全局编录服务器上存储每个属性的公用名。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d9858-130">The following C# example shows how to enumerate the global catalog servers in the specified <xref:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.DirectoryContext> object and print the common name of each property stored on each global catalog server to the standard console.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
  
foreach (GlobalCatalog gc in GlobalCatalog.FindAll(context))  
{  
    Console.WriteLine(gc.Name);  
  
    foreach (ActiveDirectorySchemaProperty prop in gc.FindAllProperties())  
    {  
        Console.WriteLine(prop.CommonName);  
    }  
}  
  
```
